这次再看，奖金230WU，我第一反应是奖金怎么这么少？但是又一想就算500WU，我现在的感觉也是奖金很少，分给冠军队伍一个人也没多少。

name: pseudo 🇺🇦
fullText:
Have spent a couple days in Korea so far. 

If you’re coming for KBW, here’s my advice as a westerner who is getting adjusted:

1. Download Kakaomap. Google Maps doesn’t work for walking directions and is weak for public transport, but Kakaomap handles both.

2. Learn how to use https://t.co/Hjfgn6Wbrx
